problemDetailDocument.title: Duplicate key error: 7017909699 PRODUCT_CON_02
problemDetailDocument.detail: Every record on a table must have a unique key.  There's already a record whose key matches the value(s) you specified.  If you want to save this information, you must either change the key to be something that doesn't already exist OR display the existing record and change it.

serverMessage.longDescription: Every record on a table must have a unique key.  There's already a record whose key matches the value(s) you specified.  If you want to save this information, you must either change the key to be something that doesn't already exist OR display the existing record and change it.
